BIRNIN KEBBI – The governor of Sokoto State and presidential hopeful, Aminu Waziri Tambuwal on Tuesday visited Kebbi state as part of consultation tour aimed at cementing relationships with the excos and teaming supporters of peoples democratic party in Kebbi state and seek their support and endorsement on presidential ambition. Governor Aminu was received by top party echelons in persons of the former minister of defence Dr Bello Haliru, retired general Bello Sarkin Yaki, former minister for special duties Kabiru Tanimu Turaki and retired general Ishaya Bamaiyi and a host other party stalwarts. Earlier in his welcome address, the chief host and the party elder Dr Bello Haliru formerly welcomes Tambuwal to Kebbi which he described as home to the visiting governor, he added that, the situation of the country needs a courageous, dedicated and selfless leader like Tambuwal to rescue the country from the untold hardship Nigerians are passing through under Buhari led government. Sanwo-Olu Congratulates Oluyomi Finnih, GAC Member, At 80 Anyim’s Presidential Bid Boosted As 85 Pressure Groups… He explained that, president Buhari has plunged the nation into worst moments in the nations history, he has allowed wanton killings, crashed the economy, created job loses and brought about system decay which has collapsed all sectors in the country. Bello who pledged total support of Kebbi PDP to Tambuwal assured of total votes from party’s delegates “You are at home so relax we have endorsed you because we know your track records and ability to govern this country should you win which we pray you will. In his speech, the state chairman Usman Bello Suru thanked visiting governor for coming to Kebbi to seek their support, according to him Tambuwal shouldn’t have come to Kebbi because they are the ones to campaign for him “on behalf of all the state excos, local governments and National delegates we have endorsed you and welcome you home, I can assure you that you will not miss a single vote from Kebbi he said. Governor Tambuwal who spoke last thanked Kebbi PDP for the warm reception accorded him, while calling members of the party to remain united, courageous and steadfast in the rescue mission project he urge them to leave no stone unturned to save Nigeria. He added that, no one needs to be told what the situation of the country is under Buhari led APC,” how much is a bag of rice in Kebbi itself and how much was it sold under PDP government, he alleged that mister Buhari has turned Nigeria into poverty capital. POLL He disclosed that APC has failed to redeem all its campaign promises what we have now is general insecurity, hunger, joblessness poor or no education at all ,no affordable and accessible healthcare for the poor in the country and the shameful thing is that Nigeria is leading in corruption as international anti corruption agencies indicated not the opposition PDP, he charged members of PDP to continue to exhibit courage as they did during the just concluded local councils polls in Kebbi “Nigerians are waiting for PDP to take over and rescue them we cant afford to disappoint them he said.